---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<Layout title={`The Partnership — ${SITE_TITLE}`}>
	<section class="hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">The Partnership</p>
		<h1>Alignment is everything.</h1>
		<p class="lede">
			We founded this firm to solve a specific problem: the dilution of expertise in traditional advisory. We don't scale for the sake of volume; we optimize for the success of the principal.
		</p>
	</section>

	<hr />

	<section class="content-grid">
		<div class="side-label">
			<p>Our Philosophy</p>
		</div>
		<div class="main-text">
			<h2>Signal over noise.</h2>
			<p>
				Most advisory firms are built to produce "deliverables"—massive slide decks that provide plausible deniability but little direction. We focus on <strong>conviction</strong>. If we don't believe a deal should happen, we say so. Our value is in the clarity of our "No" as much as the confidence of our "Yes."
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="content-grid">
		<div class="side-label">
			<p>The Model</p>
		</div>
		<div class="main-text">
			<h2>The partner is the practitioner.</h2>
			<p>
				The industry standard is to sell with seniors and execute with juniors. We've inverted this. Every engagement is handled directly by a principal. You gain the benefit of decades of intuition and battle-hardened experience, not a templated approach from a recent MBA graduate.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="content-grid">
		<div class="side-label">
			<p>Selectivity</p>
		</div>
		<div class="main-text">
			<h2>A private mandate.</h2>
			<p>
				We operate as a boutique partnership by choice. We only accept a limited number of mandates at any given time to ensure that our focus remains absolute. We do not participate in competitive beauty contests; we work with principals who value discretion and asymmetric insight.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<p>We work with family offices, private equity principals, and independent operators.</p>
		<a class="btn primary" href="/contact">Initiate a Conversation</a>
	</section>

	<style>
		.hero {
			padding: 1rem 0 2rem 0;
		}
		.lede {
			max-width: 40rem;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}
		.content-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
			gap: 2rem;
			padding: 3rem 0;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--border));
		}
		.side-label {
			grid-column: span 3;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			color: rgb(var(--muted));
			font-weight: 600;
		}
		.main-text {
			grid-column: span 8;
		}
		.main-text h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}
		.main-text p {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			color: rgb(var(--foreground));
			line-height: 1.7;
		}
		.cta-section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.cta-section p {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			font-style: italic;
			color: rgb(var(--muted));
		}
		@media (max-width: 960px) {
			.side-label {
				grid-column: 1 / -1;
			}
			.main-text {
				grid-column: 1 / -1;
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
